  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Change Dyad Closure</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Change Dyad Closure / Change Configuration of Dyad&apos;s Assembly.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Terminology</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="9" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;"> Dyad : </para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">also known as Assur Group : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">dyad</text> is an assembly of two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> and three <text styleclass="VariableName-small">joints</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">There is one joint that joins the two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> together.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The two other joints join the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts </text>to two other <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> that are <text styleclass="VariableName-small">kinematically-defined</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> and three joints in a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">dyad</text> are <text styleclass="VariableName-small">kinematically-defined</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Assur Groups : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Another name for a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">dyad</text>&#32;</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Dyad Closures : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The different ways you can assemble the two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">dyad</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2" style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Configuration of the Dyad&apos;s Assembly</text> is a different way to express <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Dyad Closure</text>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">Types of Dyad : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Planar Dyads</text>: <text styleclass="VariableName-small">R-R-R, R-R-P, R-P-R, R-P-P, P-R-P</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Spatial Dyads</text>: <text styleclass="VariableName-small">S-S-R, S-S-P</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">R : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Revolute Joint = <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddPinJoint">Pin-Joint</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">P : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Prismatic Joint = <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddSlideJoint">Slide-Joint</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:110px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small" style="text-align:right;">S : </para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:503px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Spherical Joint = <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddBallJoint">Ball-Joint</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2" style="width:450px;">
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See more: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Dyad">Dyads</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Change Dyad Closure</para>
